menu "breadboard: bb_serialize_logfmt"

config BB_SERIALIZE_LOGFMT_F64_DECIMALS
    int "Fixed fractional digits for f64 logfmt output"
    default 6
    range 1 15
    help
        Number of fractional digits emitted for double values
        (deterministic fixed-decimal, e.g. 3.5 -> "3.500000" at the
        default of 6). No snprintf/locale involved -- purely a scale-
        and-round hand-rolled formatter, same algorithm as
        BB_SERIALIZE_JSON_F64_DECIMALS.

endmenu
